OL,4,Cannouncer remembered by club and fans
OL,6,FA man described as the "Voice of
OL,7,FLeicester City" with "boundless
OL,8,Fenergy" and an "unmistakable style and
OL,9,Fdelivery" is how the club and its fans
OL,10,Fwill remember their long-serving
OL,11,Fstadium PA announcer following his
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FBradley Varnam has been a familiar and
OL,15,Fmuch-loved voice to Foxes fans for
OL,16,Fmore than 25 years, before his death
OL,17,Fat the age of 56, after a short
OL,18,Fillness.
