OL,4,Cannouncer remembered by club and fans
OL,6,FMr Varnam served as the announcer from
OL,7,F1997, beginning at Filbert Street and
OL,8,Fcontinuing after the club's move to
OL,9,FKing Power Stadium in 2002.
OL,11,FDuring those years, the club said he
OL,12,Fhad become an enduring part of the
OL,13,Fmatchday experience for generations of
OL,14,Fsupporters.
OL,16,FIn a special tribute on their website,
OL,17,Fthe club wrote: "Over the years,
OL,18,FBradley's voice became the soundtrack
OL,19,Fto countless moments in the Club's
OL,20,Fhistory ` from the highs to the lows,
OL,21,Fand everything in between.
