OL,4,Cannouncer remembered by club and fans
OL,6,F"His presence on matchdays will be
OL,7,Fsorely missed by players, staff and
OL,8,Fsupporters alike.
OL,10,F"Away from the microphone, Bradley was
OL,11,Floved by those who knew him for his
OL,12,Funique sense of humour, his boundless
OL,13,Fenergy, his friendship and deep
OL,14,Faffection for Leicester City.
OL,16,F"He will be fondly remembered by all
OL,17,Fwho worked alongside him at club,
OL,18,Fwhere his contribution often went far
OL,19,Fbeyond his role on matchdays.
