OL,6,F"The thoughts and heartfelt
OL,7,Fcondolences of everyone at Leicester
OL,8,FCity Football Club are with Brad's
OL,9,Fwife, Sarah, his children, Zach and
OL,10,FMegan, and his many family members and
OL,11,Ffriends at this difficult time. Rest
OL,12,Fin peace, Brad ` and thank you for
OL,13,Feverything."
OL,15,FDuring his time at the club, Mr Varnam
OL,16,Fsaw seen an array of managers and
OL,17,Fplayers come and go.
