OL,6,FHe would have been announcing at the
OL,7,Fstadium during several ups and downs
OL,8,Fover the years, seeing the club go
OL,9,Fdown into the third tier, before
OL,10,Fbouncing back and getting promoted
OL,11,Fback into the Premier League.
OL,13,FHe also saw Leicester became Premier
OL,14,FLeague Champions in 2016 and win the
OL,15,FFA Cup in 2021.
OL,17,FHe also would have seen some of the
OL,18,Fbiggest clubs in Europe come to
OL,19,FLeicester when they played in the
OL,20,FChampions League, including Porto,
OL,21,FSevilla and Atletico Madrid.
